testsuite.name: au.org.ala.ecodata.OutputServiceSpec

testcase.name: test create output with no parent activity
createOrUpdateRecordsForOutput should not create associated Record objects when they does not contain species information
createOrUpdateRecordsForOutput should not create associated Record objects when excludeAbsenceRecord is true and individualCount is 0
createOrUpdateRecordsForOutput should not create associated Record objects when excludeAbsenceRecord is true and individualCount is '0'
createOrUpdateRecordsForOutput should not create associated Record objects when excludeAbsenceRecord is true and individualCount is '10'
createOrUpdateRecordsForOutput should not create associated Record objects when excludeAbsenceRecord is true and individualCount is null
createOrUpdateRecordsForOutput should create associated Record objects when excludeAbsenceRecord is true and individualCount is gt 1
createOrUpdateRecordsForOutput should create associated Record objects when excludeAbsenceRecord is true and individualCount field is not set
createOrUpdateRecordsForOutput should create associated Record objects when they contain species information
createOrUpdateRecordsForOutput should create a Record for general data and three for the multisightings reusing general data
createOrUpdateRecordsForOutput should create one Record only for the entry that has outputSpecies info and none for the general information that lacks it
deleteProject should soft delete the project and all related records when destroy = false
deleteProject should hard delete the project and all related records when destroy = true
